        "faq_2_answer": "The Artevive earplugs reduce up to 27 dB of harmful noise. This results in converting all the harsh noises like the wind noise down to a peaceful level. Allowing you to focus more on the ride, while still hearing the traffic around you and your intercom. You can also hold a normal conversation with the earplugs in as they don't reduce as much of the frequencies of the human voice.",
